title: The Healthy Owl Bakery Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Take-out, Bakery, Canadian
description: Bakery cafe in Waterloo opened in July 2013. Serves in-house-made baked goods as well as soups, salads, and wraps. Has fair market coffee, loose leaf tea, and Wi-Fi. Uses dairy and egg, so vegans need to specify.
